qStringExpression.qExpr:
'How many Analyzer Capacity minutes (or Capacity Time) used across given time period.
Given that Analyzer Capacity Minutes renew the first day of each month, this measure should be used with Month as a dimension
Otherwise this monthly renewal attribute should be noted.'
& IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based' 
	AND [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>0
    AND Not Sum([Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)])>0,
    '* Analyzer Capacity Minutes usage is captured historically in the logs starting in June 2019 Sense.' &
    ' Earlier versions of Sense will report Analyzer Capacity Minutes = 0 in this chart even though minutes were used historically.'
    ,'')

qMeasure.qLabel: Tokens or Access Used Last 28 Days

qMeasure.qDef:
num(
  (
  	ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-28))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)
  	+count({<[Access Type]-={'Login'}>} distinct UserId)
  )/(
  	ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=timestamp(ReloadTime()-28))"}>} distinct TOTAL UsageId)/10)
  	+count({<[Access Type]-={'Login'}>} distinct TOTAL UserId)
  )
,'0.0%')

qMetaDef.description: Count of Analyzer Access users active during given time period.
qMetaDef.title: Analyzer Access

qMeasure.qDef:
IF([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)] > 5,
	Num(([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]-[License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]-[License Unavailable Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])/[License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)],'0.0%'),'N/A')

qStringExpression.qExpr:
'Unused or "remaining available" Analyzer Capacity minutes.  '
& IF([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>5,
	chr(10) & ' To date in '& MonthName(Today(1)) & ' you have used ' & Num([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)],'#,##0') 
    & ' of ' & Num([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)],'#,##0') 
    & ' total minutes as reported at ' & ReloadTime() & '.'
& chr(10) & ' At an average of ' & Num([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))),'#,##0') & ' minutes used per day, you would ' 
& IF([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1)))>5,'run out of minutes in ' & Num(CEIL([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))))),'#,##0') & ' days.',' never run out!')
& chr(10) & chr(10) & 'Analyzer Capacity minutes reset the first day of each calendar month. '
,' ')
& ' Refer to the online help documentation: https://help.qlik.com/en-US/search/?q=analyzer+capacity+license'

Available User Access/ Unallocated Professional Access

qMeasure.qDef:
Num(
IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based',
	IF(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]-[License Quarantined Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens])>0,
    	Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]-[License Quarantined Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),0)
    ,
    IF(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Available Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens])>0,
    	Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Available Tokens])/Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens]),0)
    )
,'0%')
